<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171802>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. A. pygmaeus. A, fourth antennal segment; B, apical subsegment of fourth antennal segment; C, apical sensory organ of third antennal segment; D, body setae (a, anterior, b, posterior); E, ventral and dorsal chaetotaxy of the dens; F, mucro; G, metatrochanteral organ; H, tenaculum; I, anal valve chaetotaxy; J, posterior cephalic chaetotaxy; K, foot complex (a, first leg, b, second leg, c, third leg)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171802/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

